#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag4.7:4.1"
msgid "4.7. Sambhūtattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc291"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts291"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.7:5.1"
msgid "“Yo dandhakāle tarati,"
msgstr "Hurrying when it’s time for going slowly;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:5.2"
msgid "taraṇīye ca dandhaye;"
msgstr "Going slowly when it’s time to hurry;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:5.3"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"ayoniso (s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note174\">Ayoni</span> saṃvidhānena,"
msgstr "That fool falls into suffering"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:5.4"
msgid "bālo dukkhaṃ nigacchati."
msgstr "Because of these muddled arrangements."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc292"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts292"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.7:6.1"
msgid "Tassatthā parihāyanti,"
msgstr "Their good fortune wastes away"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:6.2"
msgid "kāḷapakkheva candimā;"
msgstr "Like the moon in the waning fortnight;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:6.3"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"āyasasyañca (bj)\" id=\"note175\">Āyasakyañca</span> pappoti,"
msgstr "They become disgraced,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:6.4"
msgid "mittehi ca virujjhati."
msgstr "And alienated from their friends."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc293"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts293"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.7:7.1"
msgid "Yo dandhakāle dandheti,"
msgstr "Going slowly when it’s time for going slowly;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:7.2"
msgid "taraṇīye ca tāraye;"
msgstr "Hurrying when it’s time to hurry;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:7.3"
msgid "Yoniso saṃvidhānena,"
msgstr "That wise person comes into happiness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:7.4"
msgid "sukhaṃ pappoti paṇḍito."
msgstr "Because of these proper arrangements."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc294"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts294"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.7:8.1"
msgid "Tassatthā paripūrenti,"
msgstr "Their good fortune flourishes"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:8.2"
msgid "sukkapakkheva candimā;"
msgstr "Like the moon in the waxing fortnight;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:8.3"
msgid "Yaso kittiñca pappoti,"
msgstr "They become famous and respected,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.7:8.4"
msgid "mittehi na virujjhatī”ti."
msgstr "Not alienated from their friends."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
